<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

<span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text">THE CAR PARK SOCIETY</span></span></span></h1></div><div id="comp-mfthvbm92" Park Society (TCPS) formed in 2025, our aim is to reveal hidden histories, restore connection, and</span></span><span style="font-family:montserrat,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span collective creativity and community empowerment</span></span><span style="color:#000000;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">.</span><span style="font-style:italic;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" between art, ritual, and activism. </span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Each activation is more than an event:&nbsp; it is a living portal where audiences become participants, stories become ceremonies, and overlooked spaces become sites of collective transformation.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div id="comp-mfte7263" class="comp-mfte7263 YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-mfte7263" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-mfte7263" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-mfte7263" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-mfte7263" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mfte7263inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mfte7263inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="comp-mfte72645" class="MazNVa comp-mfte72645 wixui-image"><div data-testid="linkElement" class="j7pOnl"><img loading="lazy" sizes="250px" srcSet="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/0794cc_d16bcba7065a42cead27649898f8851b~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_2,y_0,w_895,h_680/fill/w_250,h_192,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/Untitled%20-%206%20August%202025%2021_28.jpg 1x, https://static.wixstatic.com/media/0794cc_d16bcba7065a42cead27649898f8851b~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_2,y_0,w_895,h_680/fill/w_500,h_384,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/Untitled%20-%206%20August%202025%2021_28.jpg 2x" id="img_comp-mfte72645" src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/0794cc_d16bcba7065a42cead27649898f8851b~mv2.jpg/v1/crop/x_2,y_0,w_895,h_680/fill/w_250,h_192,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/Untitled%20-%206%20August%202025%2021_28.jpg" alt="Untitled -
